          "process_md": "&gt; **How to Register:**\n\n**Step 1:** Visit the [Digital Gujarat](https://www.digitalgujarat.gov.in/) portal. \n**Step 2:** The user should click on the &amp;quot;Click to register&amp;quot; option. Fill in all details and click on &amp;quot;Save&amp;quot;.\n&gt; **How to Log In:**\n\n**Step 1:** Visit the [Digital Gujarat](https://www.digitalgujarat.gov.in/) portal. \n**Step 2:** The user should click on the &amp;quot;Login&amp;quot; option. \n**Step 3:** Enter all details and click on &amp;quot;Login&amp;quot;.\n&gt; **How to Apply for a New Service:**\n\n**Step 1:** After logging in, select the relevant department.\n**Step 2**: Choose the specific service to apply for within that department.\n**Step 3:** Fill out all required details in the application form.\n**Step 4:** Upload, attach, or browse necessary documents. Alternatively, import documents directly from DigiLocker.\n**Step 5:** Carefully review all entered information.\n**Step 6:** Submit the application.\n**Step 7:** Once the application is completed, proceed to payment to download the certificate.\n**Step 8:** Upon successful payment, the certificate will be available for download.\n&amp;gt; **Digital Gujarat (Help Desk):**\n\nContact No: 18002335500\n<br>\n\n"
        }
